metadata.description:
GhostParty NFT 10K items + Domain name + Discord server + Twitter.

4.Launched on October 2021

Operations

Each NFT in the collection is worth 15 MATIC currently 37 of them are sold, and there are 9964 are left its value is roughly around 1,49,460 Matic. I am selling this project because I have no marketing team and I am working on some other projects so I have no time to focus on this. The new owner can sell this NFT collection and take full profit. 

What you will get?

1.GhostParty NFT project
2.Domain name 
3.Discord server
4.Twitter page

Ownership

The ownership of GhostParty NFT, website hosting,domain   will be transferred to owner of this NFT. Minting website will be modified as per the new owner suggestion. 

Endorsements

This project is one of the projects that is reviewed by the top NFT related YT channel 'NFT TIMES'.
